claim: The Bends was the only album released in 1995.
premise_source_doc_sentence: The Bends  (  stylised as the bends  )  is the second studio album by the English alternative rock band Radiohead , released on 13 March 1995 by Parlophone Records in the United Kingdom and by Capitol Records in the United States .
